Jadi, dia bukan hamba.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:24.460
Anak muda.

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.850
Adakah si bodoh tua itu berkata bila dia akan kembali?

00:08:28.070 --> 00:08:28.780
