00:11:08.910 --> 00:11:09.650
Puan Yan,

00:11:09.810 --> 00:11:10.890
jom baca surat.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:12.060
sangat baik.

00:11:12.510 --> 00:11:13.130
Surat rahsia itu

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:14.420
