00:11:19.030 --> 00:11:20.820
Saya memberitahu anda untuk berhenti bermain-main.

00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:24.010
Ibu kita nampaknya sukakan dia.

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:25.770
Pengasuh Wu,

00:11:26.180 --> 00:11:27.220
